{"id":271205,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-上海同城聚会前夕，多人受到警方骚扰威/","date":"2012-12-28T17:30:49Z","modified":"2012-12-28T17:30:49Z","title":"维权网 | 上海同城聚会前夕，多人受到警方骚扰威胁","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员王冬见、钟剑报道）本月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日下午，是上海各界再次举行同城聚会的日子，然而，不仅发布信息的微博、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">QQ</span><span>被封，警方更是骚扰威胁活跃人士，甚至直接表明不许参加聚会。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日开始，两次入狱累计坐牢</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>年的上海异议人士高晓亮被软禁在家无法出门；汪建华不仅受到警方的骚扰威胁，电脑也被警察拿走检查；胡可师受到工商部门及辖区派出所的上门骚扰威胁，先是派出所警察警告胡可师不要参与同城公民聚餐活动，否则会有麻烦。接着工商局的人说：我们接到举报，说你卖假酒。需要稽查，周末须有本人在场。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>谢丹和李化平的微博因发布同城公民聚会信息被封，目前无法联系二人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海同城公民聚会发布通知如下：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海本月公民同城聚餐<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>地点：甲私房菜馆<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>时间：<span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span>日下午<span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">00</span></span></div>\n<div><span>详细地址：上海市徐汇区番禺路<span lang=\"EN-US\">1207</span>号（位于凯旋路与吴中东路、番禺路交叉口）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>地铁<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>号线、<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>号线、<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>号线宜山路站下后沿凯旋路往西步行<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>分钟。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>地铁<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>号线、<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>号线、<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>号线虹桥路站下后沿凯旋路往东步行<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>分钟。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>联系电话：<span lang=\"EN-US\">021-64481078</span></span></div>\n<div><span>本期主题：学习《宪法》。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">00</span>——<span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>座谈、茶话<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>——<span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>聚餐<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">AA</span><span>制，每人约<span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span>元。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}